local a={"Hi.","Em...","Looks like everyone else hasn\'t arrived yet... What do you want to do now?","How hard working.","The festival is very interesting! There\'s delicious snacks, pretty lanterns... and fireworks! Where are we going first?","What are we doing next?","Hehe!","The festival is getting more and more lively!","There you are! You\'ve kept me waiting you know... Happy Spring Festival!","There\'re so many people at the festival, I don\'t wanna lose you in the crowd, so... stay close to me?","Hum... Do I look weird in this?","After walking around for so long, I\'m steaming, so hot!","No one has set foot in my domain for hundreds of years, so it must be fate that brought you to me.","Gawrr—! Wh-what, I\'m sounding like a small animal? Hold your tongue, I\'m undoubtedly a great dragon god!","Hm! I\'m in this form only because I haven\'t received any offering in the past hundreds of years so I can\'t show you my true form. Human, if you worship me sincerely, I will return your favor once I regain my power.","Good, good, I can trust you to learn and meet my expectations.","Did the servants I lend you work in a satisfactory manner? If yes, don\'t forget the right offerings.","Seeing me in this form without fear, that\'s impressive for a human.","You can touch, but beware of my flames, they are scorching hot.","Take these rewards, you have earned them.","A saying among human females is that \"A woman will adorn herself for those who bring joy to her.\" I tidied myself up today for you, do you like it?","Huh? Is there anything you want to do together? Waiting like this is boring, don\'t you think?","Could it be that you want me to be even more humanlike? Then you need to put more effort, heehee.","Hah! As expected of the person I have chosen.","Come closer, let me see your face... Haha, you are lovely as always.","Such beautiful scenery in front of us, I\'m sure there is something you want to tell me, no?","I may have myriads of servants, but you are the only one I have allowed in my heart. Come here, look into my eyes... How does it feel being my most beloved person?","What? Did I not give you enough favors? Heehee, you are such a greedy person.","The broth has such a rich flavor and smooth texture! I can\'t get enough of it... Ahem, {name}, I regret to inform you that your offering does not meet the standards of Li Yang, Lady of the Snake Palace. Make a few more improved versions, and I will continue to help you with the taste-testing.","Rashly touching Lady Li Yang\'s personal attendant? Careful, you might get cursed to lose at mahjong for a whole year. Huh? Am I just trying to scare you? Heh, what do you think?","Most of the restaurants in One Han City have decent food, but their service needs some improvement. {name}, you are hereby tasked with warning them: the next time I visit, they better not recommend the children\'s menu to me again.","I\'m surprised such a thing could even be achieved with a mortal body...","The trials of Lady Li Yang have never been easy. Don\'t be discouraged.","Oh, {name}, it\'s you. I found a new recipe, it calls for melted snow from the far north, lingzhi mushrooms from the mountain peaks, and a chef with a pure heart... If it will satisfy Lady Li Yang, surely you\'ll be able to make this, won\'t you?","Zzz... Zzz... There\'s nothing unusual with a little extra sleep, I did sacrifice my hibernation to guide you in preparing a proper offering, after all... Hiss... But I warn you... you may not be rash... or lazy... while I\'m sleeping...","Hiss... Avert your eyes! Don\'t think I don\'t know what you\'re thinking – I won\'t just grow bigger after a few days of some random feeding... I mean, focus on the offerings, and when Lady Li Yang\'s divine power gets restored, she might just grace us with a personal visit and reward.","Nicely done, you possess a spark of the Snake Clan\'s brilliance. You\'ll succeed in whatever you do.","A minor blunder. You won\'t lose heart over this, will you, {name}?","Come here, {name}. In recognition of your diligent work in preparing the ritual every day, on behalf of Lady Li Yang, I have generously granted you the privilege of sharing in the feast.","I detest winter. The cold seeps into my entire body, and my temperature keeps dropping. Hey, {name}, come closer... Come on, closer! Hehe, finally – nice and warm. Okay, to fulfill your task of keeping me warm, you mustn\'t stray even an inch from me during these days!","Mmm... Juicy and delicious, very nice... This roast duck was well cooked to a standard befitting my status... Huh? Isn\'t it only right that I sample the offering for Lady Li Yang in advance? Don\'t question what doesn\'t concern you – just make sure the next offering is as good as this one, and you\'ll be rewarded handsomely.","You seem to have gained quite a bit of experience, {name}. Excellent, I trust Lady Li Yang will be pleased as well.","Even snakes will miss their prey at times. Just keep trying.","{name}, get over here, quickly! I bought the best milk tea in the mortal realm! It\'s super-charged with taro mash, mochi, bobas, grass jelly, and red beans! Why are there so many ingredients in it? Hiss... A snake doesn\'t pick and choose – whatever the shop had, I requested, naturally. Fine... If you insist, I guess I can let you have a little taste.","Roast duck, roast chicken, roast goose, braised pork, braised duck, chicken in soy sauce, cured meat, century eggs... What are you laughing at, {name}? This is a list of delicacies shared by Lady Li Yang herself. Isn\'t this the most authoritative recipe book in the mortal realm?","Once the ritual is complete, you won\'t see me again. Look at you, all sad and upset. I suppose you\'ve already fallen for my charm? Most people fear snakes, but you were willing to get close to us... Once the ice and snow melt, Lady Li Yang will come to the mortal realm in person. She\'ll like you too, I\'m sure of it.","Choosing you to prepare the ritual was the right decision.","I\'ll take your naughty behavior as a sign that you\'re trying to keep me here a little longer on purpose.","Surprised by the true form of the Lady of the Snake Palace? Your earthly hospitality has pleased me greatly. Now with the ritual complete, I\'ll be traveling to the four corners of the world. But don\'t think this is your chance to escape my clutches – I could hardly bear to part with such a delectable offering like you. We will meet again...!","So, this is where jobs are assigned! Looking forward to working with you.","Always check to make sure your togs are in apple-pie order... especially your shoelaces!","Okay, that\'s enough rest for now. Time to saddle up, I have to wrangle all the faith I can today!","It\'s important to eat something after exercising – even deities get hungry, you know! You should eat too, {name}!","I\'m even more raring to go than I was before! Okay, on to the next job!","We meet again! I\'m in superb condition today, I think I could run ten miles without breaking a sweat!","No... I can\'t use my divine power, that would be cheating. But dang it, I really want to work three jobs at once...","Delivery jobs are my specialty! Just start by running, and you can\'t go wrong!","What a haul! At this rate, this will be all wrapped up in no time!","Ooh, very nice! To borrow a human expression... I think we\'re both learning the ropes!","Hey! I\'ve been waiting for you! Let\'s sprint to that finish line with everything we\'ve got today!","I see... So, humans these days are pretty fussy about their \"contracts\"... Those are basically the same as \"covenants,\" right?","After running around One Han City the last few days, I pretty much know it like the back of my hand! Can I go to your house sometime too, {name}?","Brrr... It\'s freezing outside today... Huh? Yeah, this outfit from the Horse Palace is a bit flimsy... But that\'s all good! I just have to keep moving to keep warm!","Okay, the divine power is surging through me now! I\'ve got to keep up the pace from here on out!","You mapped out today\'s route for me? Wow... that\'s a big help! I\'ll do my best out there!","Huh? A towel? You\'re giving this to me to dab the sweat? Thanks! Don\'t forget that you need to balance work and rest too!","Hah... Mmm... Zzz... Huh? Oh! I wasn\'t sleeping! I was just resting my eyes... Ahaha... Sleeping on the job would be a disaster, after all...","Whoa, whoa, whoa, I overshot?! {name}, look out! Make way, make way!!","Nice, I\'ll be able to run even faster now! Now if I could just get over the carsickness...","Maybe I should buy a few souvenirs to take back from One Han City... Oh, there you are! What do you think I should get?","What\'s this energy drink you gave me...? Oh, I see, it\'s something you drink to instantly recover your vitality! Thank you!","Whenever I\'m feeling tired, just seeing a person\'s smiling face gives me energy! Humans are so darn cute when they\'re hard at work... That includes you, {name}.","Good work today! And you know what they say: Work hard, play hard. So, let\'s go hit the gym!","Heh, my divine power is now fully charged. Get ready to witness my ultimate form!","Okay, here we go! Just a teeny bit of work left now. Come on, let\'s push it over the finish line!","One, two, one, two... Huh? I\'m stretching, of course. If I want to give work my all, I have to stay in peak physical and mental condition!","I feel like my ears have been flicking constantly the last couple of days... Oh! It must be a sign of good luck, like when humans get an itchy right palm?","I\'m back! Just thinking about being almost done gets me all fired up again! Same with humans, right? There\'s always that burst of motivation right before work or school ends!"}return a